Before you begin, open the install.sh file and review the settings section. 

If you don't want to install the desktop packages, change InstallDesktop=yes to InstallDesktop=no

1.  Open up a terminal
2.  cd into the directory in which this README file is located.
3.  Execute ./install.sh
4.  Enter your password and hit enter
5.  Respond to any prommpts that come up, and the installation will complete on its own
